    "body": "I think the correct way is to have 10k ETH at block X and 0 at block X-1 and before.\r\n\r\nIf you have 10k ETH only after X+1, then the transaction that occurred in block X+1 wouldn't be valid since the sender balance is 0 given that the sender is one of the test accounts.",
